  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505470/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1764234080\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505470/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1764234080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505470/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1764234080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505470/extras/e80a5348eae7116caefc18db0630bba9.avif?t=1764234080\" width=610 height=131 /></span><br>Features<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore locations with a variety of traps.<br></li><li>Shoot at dangerous opponents.<br></li><li>Open the doors.<br></li><li>Shoot turrets (homing guns).<br></li><li>Teleport the spaceship to the next level.<br></li><li>Shoot and Dodge bullets.<br></li><li>Destroy enemies, collect first aid kits and teleport the ship to a new level.<br></li><li>Learn the level and destroy your opponents.<br></li><li>Complete levels and get achievements.<br></li><li>Shoot your opponents and collect first aid kits.<br></li><li>Teleport the ship to a new level and get achievements.<br></li><li>Destroy your opponents enjoy the victory and go to the next level.</li></ul><br>History:<br>Space pilot Arnold goes to a space base to study secret data, but falls into an insidious trap of evil aliens.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1505470/extras/372183449635015f6e2986ce54ca1210.poster.avif